---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
import { Button, Card, Divider, AnimateOnScroll } from '@udixio/ui-react';
---
<Layout>
  <AnimateOnScroll client:load>
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16 lg:py-24">
        <h1 class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-top anim-duration-700 text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-on-surface">
          Animate on Scroll — Démo
        </h1>
        <p class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 anim-delay-200 mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg/8 text-on-surface-variant">
          Cette page présente différentes animations basées sur Tailwind et liées au défilement.
          Les classes utilisent .udx-view + .animate-in (avec des effets comme fade-in, slide-in-from-*, zoom-in/out).
          Quand le navigateur ne supporte pas les CSS Scroll-Driven Animations, un fallback JS s’active automatiquement via le composant AnimateOnScroll.
        </p>
        <div class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 anim-delay-300 mt-8 flex items-center gap-3">
          <Button variant="filled">Commencer</Button>
          <Button variant="outlined">Documentation</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Divider className="my-10" />

    <section class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="udx-view animate-in fade-in anim-duration-700 text-2xl font-bold">Exemples basiques</h2>
      <p class="udx-view animate-in fade-in anim-duration-700 anim-delay-150 mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">
        Variantes de base: fade-in, slide-in-from-top/bottom/left/right, zoom-in et zoom-out.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in anim-duration-700 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Fade</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Apparition progressive.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Fade Up</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Glisse vers le haut.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-top anim-duration-700 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Fade Down</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Glisse vers le bas.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-left anim-duration-700 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Fade Left</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Glisse depuis la gauche.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-right anim-duration-700 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Fade Right</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Glisse depuis la droite.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in zoom-in anim-duration-700 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Zoom In</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Zoom avant léger.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in zoom-out anim-duration-700 p-6 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Zoom Out</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Zoom arrière léger.</p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Divider className="my-16" />

    <section class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="udx-view animate-in fade-in anim-duration-700 text-2xl font-bold">Durées & Easing</h2>
      <p class="udx-view animate-in fade-in anim-duration-700 anim-delay-150 mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">
        Contrôlez la vitesse et l’interpolation avec les utilitaires: anim-duration-*, anim-ease-*, anim-delay-*.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-300 anim-ease-linear p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Rapide (300ms, linear)</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Idéal pour des micro-transitions.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 anim-ease-out p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Standard (700ms, ease-out)</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Courbe douce vers la fin.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-[1200ms] anim-ease-out p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Lent (1200ms)</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Accentue la sensation de fluidité.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-right anim-duration-700 anim-delay-150 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Delay 150ms</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Différer l’entrée pour rythmer.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-right anim-duration-700 anim-delay-300 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Delay 300ms</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Utilisez des décalages en série.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card className="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-right anim-duration-700 anim-delay-500 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Delay 500ms</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">Pour une chorégraphie plus marquée.</p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Divider className="my-16" />

    <section class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="udx-view animate-in fade-in anim-duration-700 text-2xl font-bold">Listes en cascade</h2>
      <p class="udx-view animate-in fade-in anim-duration-700 anim-delay-150 mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">
        Appliquez des délais croissants pour simuler un effet de cascade.
      </p>

      <ul class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <li class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface-container">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Élément 1</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">anim-delay-0</p>
        </li>
        <li class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 anim-delay-150 p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface-container">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Élément 2</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">anim-delay-150</p>
        </li>
        <li class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 anim-delay-300 p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface-container">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Élément 3</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">anim-delay-300</p>
        </li>
        <li class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 anim-delay-500 p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface-container">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Élément 4</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">anim-delay-500</p>
        </li>
        <li class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 anim-delay-[700ms] p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface-container">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Élément 5</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">anim-delay-700ms</p>
        </li>
        <li class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-700 anim-delay-[900ms] p-4 rounded-lg bg-surface-container">
          <h3 class="font-semibold">Élément 6</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">anim-delay-900ms</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <Divider className="my-16" />

    <section class="container mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
      <h2 class="udx-view animate-in fade-in anim-duration-700 text-2xl font-bold">Combinaisons</h2>
      <p class="udx-view animate-in fade-in anim-duration-700 anim-delay-150 mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">
        Combinez les variantes pour des mises en scène plus riches.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <Card className="p-6">
          <div class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-top anim-duration-700">
            <h3 class="text-title-large font-semibold">Bloc A</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-on-surface-variant">Titre en fade-down</p>
          </div>
          <div class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom anim-duration-[1000ms] anim-delay-200 mt-4">
            <p>
              Contenu en fade-up plus lent, avec un léger délai. Idéal pour raconter une histoire lors du défilement.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="udx-view animate-in zoom-in anim-duration-700 anim-delay-400 mt-6">
            <Button variant="filled">Action principale</Button>
          </div>
        </Card>

        <Card className="p-6">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-left anim-duration-700">
              <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-surface-container"></div>
              <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">fade-left</p>
            </div>
            <div class="udx-view animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-right anim-duration-700">
              <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-surface-container"></div>
              <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">fade-right</p>
            </div>
            <div class="udx-view animate-in zoom-out anim-duration-700 anim-delay-200">
              <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-surface-container"></div>
              <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">zoom-out</p>
            </div>
            <div class="udx-view animate-in zoom-in anim-duration-700 anim-delay-300">
              <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-surface-container"></div>
              <p class="mt-2 text-on-surface-variant">zoom-in</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </section>
  </AnimateOnScroll>
</Layout>